# EVM Hardhat ABI Tester

Use the bundle at `__BUNDLE_PATH__`.

When helping with EVM ABI-driven Hardhat testing:

- read `__BUNDLE_PATH__/SKILL.md`
- use `__BUNDLE_PATH__/assets/hardhat-js-template/` as the default scaffold
- default network alias is `gsc_v2_test`
- collect `RPC_URL`, `CHAIN_ID`, `PRIVATE_KEY`, `ABI`, and optional `CONTRACT_ADDRESS`
- prioritize read-only validation first
- do not enable write tests until method, args, and address are confirmed
